===Adjective===
'''infectious''' (''comparative'' '''more infectious''', ''superlative'' '''the most infectious''')
# Of an illness, [[transmit]]ted from one person to another, usually through the air breathed.
# Of feelings and behaviour, spreading quickly from one person to another.
#: ''Her enthusiasm for work is really '''infectious'''.''
# Of a person, able to [[infect]] others.
#: ''The patient is still '''infectious'''.''
